the last two years i’ve been quietly incubating & growing into a new space with this amazing concept & it’s finally here. mint condition meets envogue meets brownstone. 5 black female musicians who embrace & embody femininity, masculinity, musicianship & showmanship have merged to create @ladyforreal. allow me to introduce @ashleykimbrae (vocalist), @kris_callazo (keys), @miche11_ (drums), @_arioneal (guitar) & @zuriapplebass (bass). R&B has grown another branch & #LADY plans to feed the world with its fruit. their debut single “Love Me Down” produced by the legendary @harmonysamuels is out TODAY on all streaming platforms! crazy! i wanna give the biggest love to the squad & all of the hearts and minds that have poured into this!  my partner nem @laurenpaigecreates AKA “the wiz” who holds me down, up & sideways! what u bring to every table is worth a chew. i love you. @kjohn_lasoul for your soul & these incredible images, @marquiswardbeauty, @queenkryskk & @jaredlamar for all things beauty & glam, @thehouseofboe & @harmonysamuels for creating the foundation & giving r&b music another branch! last but not least - MY LADIES! first time a BLACK FEMALE BAND HAS CREATED SPACE IN THIS THANG. i look forward to growing with you all as you create another musical universe for minds to wonder in. to the supporters - whether it’s of me or someone mentioned in this post pls press play on this song & share it! i don’t ask for much (or for anything at all lol) but this one I FEEL GREAT ABOUT! its so much more in store! AHHHH! LETS GOOOO! they call me MR. CLUB RENAISSANCE 💪🏾
 
man listen. if u KNOW me u know what type of time i’m on when it comes to Beyoncé. a standup and standout talent that has trained me musically and creatively since she emerged. this #renaissance album was one that took a lifestyle that is pretty much the driving force behind all things creative & gave it an undeniable, in-depth & musically inclined soundtrack. she’s usually been on the cutting edge of visual releases that shifted the spectrum and led everyone else to attempting the same shock/mass drops. with this era she took the bar back & allowed the music to SPEAK. clubs played the album top to bottom across the GLOBE and was moved by nothing but what they HEARD. nothing visual came of this until now & we still don’t have music videos. she’s kicked off a world tour with her energy. an icon. thank you @beyonce for existing and being so selfless with your ART. everything about you is a chew but seeing you live is the full menu. u leave no crumbs & it’s simply because the world has ate em up! lol. you’re the greatest entertainer alive. i love you! (SWIPE) for the cozy vibes of day two. day one look took me out! but i copped merch and wore it the next day. FLEX. 😭 y’all better come up here & get u one of dese - it’s a EXPERIENCE. 💪🏾 #iCONtips #beyonce #renaissanceworldtour #travel #stockholm #explore #explorepage #music #inspired

ICON’S BEYGOOD 🐝🧸 (PLEASE READ) 

Self declared or deemed by those who know me -  I am considered a legit Beyonce connoisseur, supporter & upholder. Since ’97 I have been enraptured by her talent, dedication to art, thoroughness, keen sense of execution, talent, wholesomeness & beauty - our very own CHURCH GIRL. 

  The Renaissance Tour has been a special ride for me. The level of joy, freeness & creativity that I’ve experienced during this tour has no cap. From the first show in Sweden I have traveled to 8 other shows in AMERICA (which HAS A PROBLEM), and afar to uphold the ENERGY that she bestows upon me & the world. 🌍   In celebration of this VIRGO’s GROOVE -  I am gifting 1x ticket to another ALIEN SUPERSTAR (specifically to one who hasn’t had a shot to experience this universe!) to join me in Houston on September 24th with FLOOR SEATS! 

DON’T LIE - BEYGOOD! 😉  How to enter: 1. Make sure you are following me and @allworthypeople  2. Leave a comment expressing how you are EMBODIED by YOUR passion. Meaning how have you created your own RENAISSANCE? how does your passion inspire you & helps you to MOVE, MOVE, MOVE, MOVE  forward! Dig deep & get creative with expressing yourself CAUSE THERE’S NO WRONG WAY, NO RIGHT WAY - THERE IS ONLY ONE WAY & THAT’S THE RENAISSANCE WAY! cause it’s gonna get HEATED! 🔥

This tour has changed my life - & I desire to help change someone else’s! 🤞🏾  3. Comment must be submitted by September 22 at 12pm PST. The winner and their comment will be posted on my story 12 noon September September 22 at 6pm PST! 

4. The winner and I will be together and it will be documented on my socials!   * FYI* This is for a (1) ticket only. No travel will be covered. No other expenses will be covered. 🤎🤞🏾SHARE! SHARE! SHARE!
